Class Plant

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Skullcab, Sneezewort
    public abstract class Plant
extends Organism
    A class of plants as a special kind of organism. These organisms do not mind overlapping. They are not effected (meaning damaged or healed) by geological features.
